Hint informing the user that turning on a specific setting will allow the app to default to getting article content from offline packs. The included link will take the user to the Settings screen.

* "Prefer offline content" is {{msg-wm|Wikipedia-android-strings-preference title prefer offline content}}
* "Settings" is {{msg-wm|Wikipedia-android-strings-settings item preferences}}
